name: Mackenzie Canadian Short Term Fixed Income ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks a steady flow of income with an emphasis on capital preservation. The Fund investing mainly in fixed income securities issued in Canada by governments, government related entities and corporations. It will generally invest in high-quality fixed income securities with relatively shorter terms to maturity and may hold up to 40 Percentage of its assets in foreign investments.
